node_6.subject: Klaus Mueller
node_6.description: This is Klaus Mueller's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am, have breakfast at the Hobb Cafe at 9:00 am, get to know the other participants in the Love Ville program and start forming connections from 10:00 am to 12:00 pm, have a lunch at 12:00 pm, explore the Ville Village and its surroundings from 1:00 pm to 5:00 pm, have dinner at the Hobb Cafe at 6:00 pm, engage in evening activities and conversations with the other participants from 7:00 pm to 10:00 pm.
